            "id": 5982462,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 斐成(3313)大漲7.06%，報14.4元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>斐成(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3313:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3313\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3313-TW</a>)16日12:14股價上漲0.95元，報14.4元，漲幅7.06%，成交559張。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>斐成(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3313:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3313\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3313-TW</a>)所屬產業為其他業，主要業務為住宅及大樓開發租售業務。建材批發。綜合營造。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價下跌0.37%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲3.34%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><div class=\"dzbcd51\"></div><div class=\"m1aaic49\"></div><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+24 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+105 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-81 張</li> <li>融資增減：0 張</li> <li>融券增減：0 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
