            "title": "盤中速報 - 太極(4934)股價拉至漲停，漲停價11.25元，成交967張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>太極(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4934:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4934\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4934-TW</a>)16日12:06上漲1元，股價漲停報11.25元，委買1張、委賣272張，成交967張。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為太陽能電池。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>太極(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4934:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4934\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4934-TW</a>)近5日股價下跌1.44%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲5.78%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><div class=\"dzbcd51\"></div><div class=\"m1aaic49\"></div><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+261 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+243 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+18 張</li> <li>融資增減：-10 張</li> <li>融券增減：0 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
